works.complaint:
Please be advised that it has been brought to my  
attention that www.windsorphotobooth.co has made unwarranted and defamatory  
attacks against Snapshot Pod, LLC on www.windsorphotobooth.co.

Snapshot Pod, LLC is a well respected photo booth rental company serving  
customers in North Texas. We have established a well founded reputation for  
the quality of our services and your unwarranted actions and baseless  
accusations have damaged that reputation and adversely affected our  
business.

www.windsorphotobooth.co has posted, or permitted to be posted, many  
willfully false and misleading comments about Snapshot Pod, LLC. Examples  
of the defamatory statements include:

- This (Snapshot Pod) is no different than any other photo booth.  In fact,  
it is worst!
- Ten times worst than the full enclosure booths.
- Because it’s not even a photo booth.
- This is laughable and perhaps a step backwards from what we are used to  
at weddings.

The above statements made in reference to Snapshot Pod, LLC are utterly  
false and without merit, and they are defamation per se in that they depict  
Snapshot Pod, LLC as an inferior company and inferior product in the  
marketplace.

Attempts to spread libelous and defamatory material about Snapshot Pod, LLC  
has caused serious and irreparable injury to the company, its reputation,  
and its business.
